OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a
OL,6,Fbright and warm evening, low cloud
OL,7,Fwill move back in overnight to bring
OL,8,Fmist and hill fog in some areas.
OL,9,FStaying dry and warm overnight. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FLow cloud will burn back
OL,13,Fduring the morning to give sunny
OL,14,Fskies. Feeling very warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine, with light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,18,FStaying dry and increasingly hot
OL,19,Fthrough the outlook. Plenty of strong
OL,20,Fsunshine and light winds, with some
OL,21,Fwarm nights too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
